’Щ@a63c157d229e0f2c63fba461fe331300c02963683bfc560110c07b764cc47158ЪTTitle: title: format pattern
Path: Examples
Content:
Print filenames with their sizes
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> ls | format pattern '{name}: {size}'


```
Print elements from some columns of a table
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[col1, col2]; [v1, v2] [v3, v4]] | format pattern '{col2}'
в•­в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”¬в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв•®
в”‚ 0 в”‚ v2 в”‚
в”‚ 1 в”‚ v4 в”‚
в•°в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”ґв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв•Ї


```
Escape braces by repeating them
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> {start: 3, end: 5} | format pattern 'if {start} < {end} {{ "correct" }} else {{ "incorrect" }}'
if 3 < 5 { "correct" } else { "incorrect" }

```
